he metrics to track hits versus misses in the TenantKeyManager.\n\nI also notice credential deletion and access operations aren't being audited at all, which is a significant gap. The cache maintenance timer could fail silently if key derivation throws, and the credentialInjector is tracking files but never exposing that count as a metric.\n\nNow I'm working through the implementation details for these observability improvements.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1593,"cache_read_input_tokens":39761,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1593},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6b375ece-41c0-48fe-9151-de360e723e96","uuid":"e574b09f-3070-47cd-9beb-b962e677a1d5"}
